<!-- ============ WHY TEAMWORK ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Why Teamwork</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Build technology that touches <span class="gradient-text">millions.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">"Nothing touches more lives more often than retail." Every feature you build, every line of code you ship, affects how people shop in 40+ countries — from luxury boutiques in Paris to stadium shops in Denver to pet stores in Mexico City.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-world"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Global impact, real customers</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Your work powers ASICS, Acne Studios, The Row, Petco, the Colorado Rockies, and The Broad. These aren't hypothetical users — they're real brands relying on what you build every single day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-code"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Hard problems, not busywork</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Native RFID that tracks 147K+ EPCs in real time. AI that makes associates instant experts. Offline POS that never drops a transaction during a 50,000-fan halftime rush. These are the problems you'll solve here.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-users-group"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Founder-led, not VC-driven</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Michael Mauerer has been building retail technology for 30+ years. No revolving-door leadership, no pivot-of-the-quarter. The roadmap is driven by customer needs and long-term vision, not investor pressure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

