      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-palette"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Product & Design</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">UX/UI for iOS, web dashboards (Cloud HQ), and the 121 Commerce AI interface. Design for luxury brands that demand Apple-standard aesthetics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-speakerphone"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Marketing</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Content, brand, demand gen, events (NRF, Shoptalk), partnerships, and the website you're looking at right now. Tell the story of the most advanced retail platform on the planet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-chart-line"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Sales & Solutions</h3>
