      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-headset"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Customer Success</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Implementation, onboarding, training, and ongoing support. Help retailers go live — from single-store pilots to Petco Mexico's 118-store, 2,000+ terminal deployment.</p>
      </div>
