        <div class="pillar-icon"><i class="ti ti-building"></i></div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Operations & Finance</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc">HR, finance, legal, and operations across 12 global offices. Keep the engine running for a company that operates in 40+ countries with enterprise clients worldwide.</p>
